==English==
==={{initialism}}===
[[Category:Internet laughter slang]]
'''ROFLMAO'''

#(''Internet'') rolling on the floor laughing my ass (arse) off, an extended form of [[ROFL]] formed by the combining with [[LMAO]]; used to indicate great amusement at something read on in a discussion group, ''etc''.

Also can mean Rolling On Floor Licking My Ass Out, although this version of the acronym is rarely, if ever, used.

